text: And thou shalt speak thus in the sight of the Lord thy God. I have taken that which was sanctified out of my house, and I have given it to the Levite, and to the stranger, and to the fatherless, and to the widow, as thou has commanded me. I have not transgressed thy commandments, nor forgotten thy precepts.
